title: Sport Watch Face Wear
summary: Additional set watch faces for Android Wear.
description: Additional set watch faces for Android Wear.- 12 style watches are made in colorful, sporty design.- some watches have rotating parts and battery indicator.- application allows you to select a color.- support for square (G Watch, Gear Live, ZenWatch etc.) and round (Moto 360, G Watch R etc.) displays.
descriptionHTML:
Additional set watch faces for Android Wear.

- 12 style watches are made in colorful, sporty design.

- some watches have rotating parts and battery indicator.

- application allows you to select a color.

- support for square (G Watch, Gear Live, ZenWatch etc.) and round (Moto 360, G Watch R etc.) displays.
comments: Needs more details Can be improved by putting more details or shadows to give dimension.  Right now, it just looks flat.  Not worth spending for.  The only watch face you'll be wanting to use is the one with blue and orange
recentChanges: Added support new Watch Face API
